title: COVID-19 Data Visualization
description: Analyzed COVID-19 case trends using Python, Pandas, and Matplotlib. Created interactive visualizations in Tableau to show global and regional trends.

title: Personal Finance Dashboard
description: Developed a web dashboard using Flask and D3.js to help students track their expenses, visualize spending habits, and manage budgets.

title: E-Commerce Recommendation System
description: Created a recommendation engine for an online store using collaborative filtering and content-based filtering techniques with Python and scikit-learn.
